rComments: He is very very knowledgeable. He made attending class the best moment of the day. His teaching style is of a story teller; he makes everything flow and easy to digest.  But he is a difficult and picky grader.  It's very hard to do well in his class, if not impossible.

Ce prof est super! Il est évidemment passionné par l'enseignement et ce qu'il enseigne. Il met beaucoup d'emphase sur l'histoire et sur la grammaire - alors, faites attention aux détails! C'est un véritable plaisir d'assister à ses cours.
Good teacher but is big on grammar and grades accordingly.
Excellent prof.  Took boring history and made it come alive.  We all loved going to class every week.  Plus, one small assignment was a breath of fresh air for us.

Good prof but not so organized when he teaches. He has a great amount of knowledge for such a young guy. Will be an excellent prof after a few more years of dealing with students. Very interesting class material.
Great class! I laughed, I cried, it was better than CATS!!!

Une vraie perle rare dans le programme de cml Français!  Il est intelligent, drôle, approchable, charismatique, terre à terre (...). He's the best thing to happen to the students of Fauteux since msn and wireless internet.
